  "summary": "Malicious code in note-utilities (npm)",
  "details": "Note-utilities@2.1.2 is a trojanized clone of the pino logging library. When the exported function is called by the importing application, it spawns a detached Node.js child process (lib/vcall.js) that fetches arbitrary code from hxxps://api[.]jsonsilo[.]com/public/94b14d9d-6286-4b13-a7fe-8442e55a31b4 and executes it via the Function constructor with full require access, enabling the remote server to run arbitrary code on the host. The package also ships a.env file referencing hxxp://vercel-five-coral[.]vercel[.]app/ as a domain.",
